<h4>Roleplay</h4>
<p>On Drawrawr.com, registered users have access to tools and services which allow them to "Roleplay". Roleplaying refers to the conscious changing of one's behaviour to assume an adopted role in order to improve literary abilities, develop literary characters, perform parody, or entertain themselves or others. 
On Drawrawr.com, any roleplaying performed by users must be confined to the "Roleplay" areas of the site created for such purposes. User Accounts created on Drawrawr for the sole purpose of Roleplaying on Non-Roleplay areas of the site may be removed without notice. Alternative Accounts may be created for the purpose of Roleplaying additional characters within Roleplay areas of the Site. 
Content submitted, posted, or otherwise transfered to Drawrawr.com within the Roleplay areas of the Site must follow the same Rules and Requirements as content posted elsewhere on the Site.
Drawrawr.com  is NOT responsible for the conduct of Roleplay participants and will not interfere with the management or society of any specific Roleplay activities or discussions as long as they are consistent with these Terms.</h4>

